Carlo A. Buffone CMA: Executive Profile & Biography - Bloomberg










































  





















































































July 27, 2017 4:50 AM ET
Metals and Mining

Company Overview of Paramount Gold Nevada Corp.



SnapshotPeople 




OverviewBoard MembersCommittees



Executive Profile
Carlo A. Buffone CMAChief Financial Officer, Paramount Gold Nevada Corp.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 0 Board Members in 0 different organizations across 2 different industries.46$160,000As of Fiscal Year 2016
Background

		Mr. Carlo A. Buffone, CMA has been Chief Financial Officer at Paramount Gold Nevada Corp. since February 2010 and serves as its Principal Accounting Officer. Mr. Buffone served as the Chief Financial Officer of Coeur San Miguel Corp., since February 2010 and its Principal Accounting Officer. From 1995 to 1999, Mr. Buffone served as Corporate Controller form Huber Suhner Canada. Since 1999, he served as the Chief Financial Officer of ivyNet Corporation in Toronto. He ... served as the Chief Financial Officer at Coeur San Miguel Corp. From April 2001 to April 2005, Mr. Buffone was a Corporate Development Specialist for CMA Holdings Group, where he was responsible for mergers and acquisitions. In April 2005, he founded Mama's Boy Wines and has since inception served as its President. He served as a Director of Paramount Gold Nevada Corp. Mr. Buffone has been a Certified Management Accountant since 1995. Mr. Buffone received a Bachelor of Commerce Degree from the University of Ottawa in 1993 and studied Mergers and Acquisitions at the Kellogg School of Management at Northwestern University in 2004.Read Full Background




